## 📌 1. Originality & Structural Authorship

All terminology, structural frameworks, and cognitive models within the MetaCrux / Meta-Cognition OS project—including but not limited to:

* Numbered modules (e.g., S-01 to S-09),
* Meta-Axioms, Cognitive Interface Maps,
* Structural Question Systems,
* Language Sealing Tools, and
* Terminology Encoding Systems,

are original creations of **Lan Yuan (MetaCrux)**. These elements are not general content but represent a **cognitive operating system and language framework**.

本项目中所有术语、结构化框架与认知模型（包括但不限于：S-01 至 S-09 编号模块、元公理结构、接口图谱、结构化提问系统、语言封装工具与术语编码系统）
均由 **Lan Yuan（MetaCrux）** 独立构建。这些内容不仅是普通文本，而是一套 **认知操作系统与语言结构框架**。

